Sentencas: In this work we have studied the elemental electrode shape and electrode - electrolyte contact microstructure influence of Internal diffusion (ID) gas electrode in solid oxide fuel cells (SOFC).
Titulo: Internal diffusion electrode-electrolyte contact shape and microstructure effect on Solid Oxide Fuel Cells (SOFC) oxygen reaction.

Sentencas: First the influence over the electrolyte effective resistance is studied.
Titulo: Internal diffusion electrode-electrolyte contact shape and microstructure effect on Solid Oxide Fuel Cells (SOFC) oxygen reaction.

Sentencas: Then the influence of the shape of the elemental contact grain of ID electrode is also studied.
Titulo: Internal diffusion electrode-electrolyte contact shape and microstructure effect on Solid Oxide Fuel Cells (SOFC) oxygen reaction.

Sentencas: Finally the influence of the electrode - electrolyte contact microstructure in the electrode response for a pure diffuse control is modelled.
Titulo: Internal diffusion electrode-electrolyte contact shape and microstructure effect on Solid Oxide Fuel Cells (SOFC) oxygen reaction.

Sentencas: From the obtained results, conclusions on the contact microstructure and electrode shape influence over the oxygen reaction of this kind of gas electrodes are commented.
Titulo: Internal diffusion electrode-electrolyte contact shape and microstructure effect on Solid Oxide Fuel Cells (SOFC) oxygen reaction.
